{
  "stem": "7273.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, you are in France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That is like day and night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The people are friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When somebody's drunk, he doesn't take the knife out and kill somebody else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, when they are drunk, they're happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so that is the whole attitude.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a completely different world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A different world, and what a nice world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wanted-- I wanted, actually, to go to the States, where I had two aunts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we fell to the Polish quota, because my husband was Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We waited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, a friend of ours came and said, look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're looking for people in Australia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you must be a tailor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tailors were wanted for Australia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband learned to sew straight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found here some far family of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they sent us a paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it took us maybe three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were called to the-- I think it was the English consulate, which worked for the Australians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it went very quickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, to get on the boat was very easy because my uncle was in a quite high position, and he dictated who comes here, who comes there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is your French aunt, the husband of the lady who lived in France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was maybe happy that the Jewish wouldn't be anymore in France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, as I said, he was a good Catholic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a very good de Gaullist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they , actually, they were very-- they're not friends of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So your aunt had married a Frenchman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But with her looks, it was-- she looked so terribly German that nobody ever would have said that she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In December '49. 3rd December '49.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
